<l>pēṇātu peṭpavē ceyyiṉuṅ koṇkaṉaik </l>
<l>kāṇā tamaiyala kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though my eyes disregard me and do what is pleasing to my husband, still will they not be satisfied unless they see him.</l>
